      <guid>http://localhost:1314/posts/emergency-fund-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Emergency Fund Guide: How Much You Need &amp;amp; Where to Keep It 
    &lt;div id=&#34;emergency-fund-guide-how-much-you-need--where-to-keep-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
